"reviewcomment":"Found this as #1 on the top five burritos of London, so I just had to give it try!<br><br>The line, for some, seems quite overwhelming during lunch time, but that is what is so fantastic about this food stand -- they provide fast, efficient, and great service, you just have to be prepared with your request as they go quickly!<br><br>I went with the fajita burrito which has peppers and onions instead of the black beans. My choice of meat was chicken, and I added sour cream, guacamole, and cheese to accompany the coriander-lime rice and veggies already included.  In my opinion, first the meat has got to be delicious, and the chicken was fantastic. But, what sets burritos apart are the veggies and optional additions -- daddy donkey has fab veggies -- cooked and prepared to the T.<br><br>All in all a fantastic spot for lunch, and place to satisfy your burrito craving! Will definitely be going back!",
