"reviewcomment":"You know those restaurants where you have to choose quality over price or price over quality??? Well NOT @ Meze Mangal !!!<br><br>Due to its high quality of freshly prepared Turkish food and an amazing value for money people are ready to spend half an hour to even an hour queuing for a table :)<br><br>Been there - done that! What strikes you though is that you won&#39;t be just left in a queue looking at other people eat their delicious food! The owner ( who also actively takes part in serving and greeting himself) was thoughtful enough to treat us with free &#39;waiting&#39; starters to which we were also able to order a drink/ wine whilst waiting. <br><br>The place is especially amazing in cold season with its grill in the middle of the room and amazing views of &#39;grilled in front of your eyes&#39; various types of fish and meat ( I can already smell it). <br><br>This restaurant serves freshly baked bread with its mouth watering meze as one of the most popular starters there. You can have as much bread with your meze as you wish without having to pay extra. And it&#39;s right from the oven! Me and my fellow diners there find it addictive. <br><br>Moreover, the portions served ( both for starters and mains) are huge and can be shared ( which most guests do there) so you can order one starter and one main for two people and no one will leave unsatisfied!!<br><br>To my delight they have recently extended the restaurant but I&#39;m sure people still queue all week round. Because it&#39;s worth it!!",
